title: Worlds without End
description: NO ONE HAS EVER SEEN ANYTHING LIKE THISAina remembers the world of centuries ago- she was there. Now she's here in the Awakened era of shadowrunners and simulations, magic and metas. And she may have brought an old nemesis along with her...This new evil is as ancient and powerful as time. It does not bend before assassins, megacorps, shamans, or dragons. Aina, Harlequin, and their fellow immortal elves might have the power to stop it... but will she be able to convince them to join the battle before it's too late?
author: Caroline Spector
